Package fr.cyu.cyfight.game.cell

Interface Cell

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Interactable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseCell
    public interface Cell
extends Interactable
    Cell is the interface for grid cells (a cell being a part of the grid on which the player moves).
    Author:
    Mika INISAN
